Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model

Class Sack

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.Sack
public class Sack extends Object
The sack class contains all the object cards and is populated when initSack() is called. Cards are held in an ArrayList and there exists methods to generate cards and to shuffle them
Author:
Luca Guffanti
